{%- comment -%}
  Section: C Product ATC Offer
  Description: Product-focused ATC offer with block-driven content, price overrides, promo-code CTA, and accordion details.
  sl-id: sl-section-product-atc-offer-v1
  Figma: https://www.figma.com/design/f1AWMl23NcBW13s8SML1B5/BKL?node-id=5774-4209&m=dev
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign sl_id = 'sl-section-product-atc-offer-v1'
  assign selected_product = section.settings.product
  if selected_product == blank and product != blank
    assign selected_product = product
  endif

  assign selected_variant = nil
  assign section_anchor_id = section.settings.sl_anchor_id
  assign media_image = section.settings.media_image
  assign media_alt = section.settings.media_alt
  assign promo_code = section.settings.promo_code | strip
  assign promo_redirect_target = section.settings.promo_redirect_target | default: 'checkout'
  assign atc_behavior = section.settings.atc_behavior | default: 'sidecart'

  if selected_product != blank
    assign selected_variant = selected_product.selected_or_first_available_variant
    if media_image == blank
      assign media_image = selected_product.featured_image
    endif
    if media_alt == blank
      assign media_alt = selected_product.title
    endif
  endif

  assign override_price = section.settings.override_price
  assign override_compare_at_price = section.settings.override_compare_at_price

  assign price_display = blank
  assign compare_display = blank

  if override_price != blank
    assign override_price_cents = override_price | times: 100
    assign price_display = override_price_cents | money
  elsif selected_variant != blank
    assign price_display = selected_variant.price | money
  endif

  if override_compare_at_price != blank and override_compare_at_price > 0
    assign override_compare_cents = override_compare_at_price | times: 100
    assign compare_display = override_compare_cents | money
  elsif selected_variant != blank and selected_variant.compare_at_price != blank and selected_variant.compare_at_price > selected_variant.price
    assign compare_display = selected_variant.compare_at_price | money
  endif

  if compare_display == price_display
    assign compare_display = blank
  endif

  assign cta_target_path = '/checkout'
  if promo_redirect_target == 'cart'
    assign cta_target_path = '/cart'
  endif
-%}

{%- capture clinical_trials_drawer_body_default -%}
  <p>Only a small percentage of dietary supplements are tested in gold-standard human clinical trials.</p>
  <p>Berkeley Life® Nitric Oxide Support has been evaluated in double-blind, placebo-controlled research demonstrating its ability to increase nitric oxide bioavailability in humans.</p>
  <p>The dietary nitrate ingredients used in our formulation are supported by a growing body of peer-reviewed clinical research validating improvements in vascular function, endothelial health, and blood pressure regulation.</p>
  <h3>The Impact of Clinical Proof</h3>
  <p>Double-blind, placebo-controlled trials (DBPCTs) are considered the gold standard in scientific research because they help ensure:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Bias elimination</li>
    <li>Control for placebo effect</li>
    <li>Validated efficacy</li>
    <li>Safety and tolerability assessment</li>
  </ul>
  <p>By studying the full nitrate formulation as it is consumed, Berkeley Life® ensures the product is evaluated for real-world effectiveness and safety - not just theoretical ingredient benefits.</p>
  <h3>Nitric Oxide Production</h3>
  <p>Berkeley Life® is formulated to increase nitric oxide through the dietary nitrate → nitrite → nitric oxide pathway.</p>
  <p>Unlike L-arginine-based supplements, this pathway remains active even when endothelial nitric oxide synthase (eNOS) declines with age.</p>
  <h3>Clinical Trial Results</h3>
  <p>In a double-blind, placebo-controlled study, participants taking Berkeley Life® demonstrated significant increases in salivary nitrite and plasma nitrite compared to placebo. Test strip readings correlated with laboratory measurements, confirming improved nitric oxide bioavailability.</p>
  <h3>Vascular &amp; Endothelial Health</h3>
  <p>Nitric oxide is essential for healthy blood vessel function. It supports vasodilation, circulation, and endothelial integrity - all of which naturally decline with age.</p>
  <h3>Clinical Trial Results</h3>
  <p>In clinical research evaluating dietary nitrate supplementation over 12 weeks, participants showed improvements in endothelial function and reductions in carotid artery stiffness, a recognized marker of cardiovascular risk. These findings support the role of nitrate-based nitric oxide in maintaining vascular flexibility and heart health.</p>
  <h3>Blood Pressure Support</h3>
  <p>Nitric oxide helps relax and widen blood vessels, supporting healthy blood pressure regulation.</p>
  <h3>Clinical Trial Results</h3>
  <p>Clinical studies of dietary nitrates have demonstrated improvements in systolic blood pressure and vascular responsiveness compared to placebo, particularly with consistent daily use over 8-12 weeks.</p>
  <h3>Energy &amp; Oxygen Efficiency</h3>
  <p>Nitric oxide plays a critical role in oxygen delivery and mitochondrial signaling. Healthy nitric oxide levels support efficient energy production and muscle performance.</p>
  <h3>Clinical Research Findings</h3>
  <p>Research on dietary nitrates has shown improvements in oxygen utilization and exercise efficiency, including reduced oxygen cost during physical activity.</p>
  <h3>Aging &amp; Nitric Oxide Decline</h3>
  <p>Nitric oxide production naturally declines with age due to oxidative stress, hormonal shifts, and reduced enzyme activity.</p>
  <p>Berkeley Life® provides a nitrate-based pathway that supports nitric oxide production independently of age-related enzymatic decline, offering measurable vascular support as the body's natural production decreases.</p>
{%- endcapture -%}

<section
  {% if section_anchor_id != blank %}id="{{ section_anchor_id }}"{% endif %}
  class="c-product-atc-offer"
  data-sl-id="{{ sl_id }}"
  data-section-id="{{ section.id }}"
  data-section-type="c-product-atc-offer"
>
  <div class="c-product-atc-offer__container">
    <div class="c-product-atc-offer__media">
      <div class="c-product-atc-offer__media-card">
        {%- if media_image != blank -%}
          {{
            media_image
            | image_url: width: 1200
            | image_tag:
              class: 'c-product-atc-offer__image',
              loading: 'lazy',
              widths: '400, 600, 800, 1000, 1200',
              alt: media_alt | escape
          }}
        {%- else -%}
          {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'c-product-atc-offer__image c-product-atc-offer__image--placeholder' }}
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          {%- if block.type == 'notice_banner' -%}
            <div class="c-product-atc-offer__notice" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              <span class="c-product-atc-offer__notice-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                {%- render 'icon-notice' -%}
              </span>
              <div class="c-product-atc-offer__notice-copy">
                {%- if block.settings.eyebrow != blank -%}
                  <span class="c-product-atc-offer__notice-eyebrow">{{ block.settings.eyebrow }}</span>
                {%- endif -%}
                {%- if block.settings.body != blank -%}
                  <span class="c-product-atc-offer__notice-body">{{ block.settings.body }}</span>
                {%- endif -%}
              </div>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="c-product-atc-offer__content">
      {%- if selected_product == blank and request.design_mode -%}
        <div class="c-product-atc-offer__empty-state">
          Select a product in the section settings to populate the offer content and CTA.
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        {%- case block.type -%}
          {%- when 'notice_banner' -%}
            {%- comment -%}Rendered inside media-card, absolute bottom{%- endcomment -%}

          {%- when 'pill_label' -%}
            {%- if block.settings.label != blank -%}
              <div class="c-product-atc-offer__pill-wrap" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
                <span class="c-product-atc-offer__pill">{{ block.settings.label }}</span>
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}

          {%- when 'reviews' -%}
            <div class="c-product-atc-offer__reviews" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              {%- if block.settings.use_judgeme and selected_product != blank and selected_product.metafields.judgeme.badge != blank -%}
                <div class="c-product-atc-offer__reviews-app">{{ selected_product.metafields.judgeme.badge }}</div>
              {%- else -%}
                <div class="c-product-atc-offer__reviews-fallback">
                  <div class="c-product-atc-offer__stars" aria-hidden="true">
                    {%- for _star in (1..5) -%}
                      {% render 'c-orange-star' %}
                    {%- endfor -%}
                  </div>
                  {%- if block.settings.rating_text != blank -%}
                    <span class="c-product-atc-offer__reviews-rating">{{ block.settings.rating_text }}</span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {%- if block.settings.reviews_text != blank -%}
                    <span class="c-product-atc-offer__reviews-count">{{ block.settings.reviews_text }}</span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>

          {%- when 'product_title' -%}
            {%- liquid
              assign display_title = block.settings.custom_title
              if display_title == blank and selected_product != blank
                assign display_title = selected_product.title
              endif
            -%}
            {%- if display_title != blank or block.settings.accent_line != blank -%}
              <div class="c-product-atc-offer__title-wrap" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
                {%- if display_title != blank -%}
                  <h2 class="c-product-atc-offer__title">{{ display_title }}</h2>
                {%- endif -%}
                {%- if block.settings.accent_line != blank -%}
                  <p class="c-product-atc-offer__accent-line">{{ block.settings.accent_line }}</p>
                {%- endif -%}
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}

          {%- when 'product_description' -%}
            {%- liquid
              assign description_content = block.settings.custom_description
              if description_content == blank and selected_product != blank
                assign description_content = selected_product.description | strip_html
              endif
            -%}
            {%- if description_content != blank -%}
              <div class="c-product-atc-offer__description" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
                {%- if block.settings.use_richtext and block.settings.custom_description != blank -%}
                  {{ block.settings.custom_description }}
                {%- else -%}
                  <p>{{ description_content }}</p>
                {%- endif -%}
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}

          {%- when 'feature_row' -%}
            {%- if block.settings.label != blank or block.settings.value != blank -%}
              <div class="c-product-atc-offer__feature-row" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
                <span class="c-product-atc-offer__feature-label">{{ block.settings.label }}</span>
                <span class="c-product-atc-offer__feature-value">{{ block.settings.value }}</span>
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}

          {%- when 'cta' -%}
            <div class="c-product-atc-offer__cta" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              {%- if price_display != blank -%}
                <div class="c-product-atc-offer__price-wrap">
                  <span class="c-product-atc-offer__price">{{ price_display }}</span>
                  {%- if compare_display != blank -%}
                    <span class="c-product-atc-offer__compare-price">{{ compare_display }}</span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}

              {%- if block.settings.caption != blank -%}
                <div class="c-product-atc-offer__caption">{{ block.settings.caption }}</div>
              {%- endif -%}

              <div class="c-product-atc-offer__cta-actions">
                {%- if selected_variant != blank and selected_variant.available -%}
                  <form
                    method="post"
                    action="{{ routes.cart_add_url }}"
                    id="ProductAtcOfferForm-{{ section.id }}"
                    class="c-product-atc-offer__form"
                    novalidate
                    data-promo-code="{{ promo_code | escape }}"
                    data-redirect-target="{{ cta_target_path }}"
                    data-atc-behavior="{{ atc_behavior }}"
                  >
                    <input type="hidden" name="form_type" value="product">
                    <input type="hidden" name="utf8" value="✓">
                    <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ selected_variant.id }}">
                    <input type="hidden" name="quantity" value="{{ section.settings.quantity | default: 1 }}">
                    <button
                      type="submit"
                      id="ProductAtcOfferSubmit-{{ section.id }}"
                      class="c-product-atc-offer__button"
                    >
                      <span class="c-product-atc-offer__button-label">{{ block.settings.button_label }}</span>
                    </button>
                  </form>
                {%- else -%}
                  <button type="button" class="c-product-atc-offer__button c-product-atc-offer__button--disabled" disabled>
                    <span class="c-product-atc-offer__button-label">{{ block.settings.sold_out_label | default: 'Sold out' }}</span>
                  </button>
                {%- endif -%}

                <div class="c-product-atc-offer__message" id="ProductAtcOfferMessage-{{ section.id }}" hidden></div>
              </div>
            </div>

          {%- when 'clinical_trials' -%}
            {%- liquid
              assign block_drawer_body = block.settings.drawer_body
              assign block_drawer_button_style = block.settings.button_style
              if block_drawer_body == blank
                assign block_drawer_body = clinical_trials_drawer_body_default
              endif
              if block_drawer_button_style == 'link'
                assign block_drawer_button_style = 'default'
              endif
            -%}
            <div class="c-product-atc-offer__trials-link-wrap" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              {%- render 'clinical-drawer',
                drawer_id: 'product-atc-offer-clinical-drawer-' | append: section.id | append: '-' | append: block.id,
                button_text: block.settings.button_label,
                button_style: block_drawer_button_style,
                drawer_title: block.settings.drawer_title,
                drawer_body: block_drawer_body,
                bg_color: block.settings.drawer_bg_color,
                text_color: block.settings.drawer_text_color
              -%}
            </div>

          {%- when 'accordion_text' -%}
            {%- assign is_open = block.settings.open_by_default -%}
            <div class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion{% if is_open %} c-product-atc-offer__accordion--open{% endif %}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              <button
                class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-trigger"
                type="button"
                aria-expanded="{{ is_open }}"
                aria-controls="ProductAtcOfferAccordion-{{ block.id }}"
              >
                <span class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-title">{{ block.settings.title }}</span>
                <span class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              </button>
              <div class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-body" id="ProductAtcOfferAccordion-{{ block.id }}" role="region">
                <div class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-content">
                  {{ block.settings.content }}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          {%- when 'accordion_ingredients' -%}
            {%- assign is_open = block.settings.open_by_default -%}
            <div class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion{% if is_open %} c-product-atc-offer__accordion--open{% endif %}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              <button
                class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-trigger"
                type="button"
                aria-expanded="{{ is_open }}"
                aria-controls="ProductAtcOfferAccordion-{{ block.id }}"
              >
                <span class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-title">{{ block.settings.title }}</span>
                <span class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              </button>
              <div class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-body" id="ProductAtcOfferAccordion-{{ block.id }}" role="region">
                <div class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-content c-product-atc-offer__accordion-content--ingredients">
                  {%- for index in (1..5) -%}
                    {%- liquid
                      assign ingredient_title_key = 'ingredient_title_' | append: index
                      assign ingredient_text_key = 'ingredient_text_' | append: index
                      assign ingredient_image_key = 'ingredient_image_' | append: index
                      assign ingredient_title = block.settings[ingredient_title_key]
                      assign ingredient_text = block.settings[ingredient_text_key]
                      assign ingredient_image = block.settings[ingredient_image_key]
                    -%}
                    {%- if ingredient_title != blank or ingredient_text != blank or ingredient_image != blank -%}
                      <div class="c-product-atc-offer__ingredient">
                        <div class="c-product-atc-offer__ingredient-image-wrap">
                          {%- if ingredient_image != blank -%}
                            {{
                              ingredient_image
                              | image_url: width: 160
                              | image_tag:
                                class: 'c-product-atc-offer__ingredient-image',
                                loading: 'lazy',
                                widths: '64, 96, 128, 160',
                                alt: ingredient_title | escape
                            }}
                          {%- endif -%}
                        </div>
                        <div class="c-product-atc-offer__ingredient-copy">
                          {%- if ingredient_title != blank -%}
                            <p class="c-product-atc-offer__ingredient-title">{{ ingredient_title }}</p>
                          {%- endif -%}
                          {%- if ingredient_text != blank -%}
                            <div class="c-product-atc-offer__ingredient-text">{{ ingredient_text }}</div>
                          {%- endif -%}
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    {%- endif -%}
                  {%- endfor -%}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          {%- when 'accordion_image' -%}
            {%- assign is_open = block.settings.open_by_default -%}
            <div class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion{% if is_open %} c-product-atc-offer__accordion--open{% endif %}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              <button
                class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-trigger"
                type="button"
                aria-expanded="{{ is_open }}"
                aria-controls="ProductAtcOfferAccordion-{{ block.id }}"
              >
                <span class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-title">{{ block.settings.title }}</span>
                <span class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              </button>
              <div class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-body" id="ProductAtcOfferAccordion-{{ block.id }}" role="region">
                <div class="c-product-atc-offer__accordion-content c-product-atc-offer__accordion-content--image">
                  {%- if block.settings.image != blank -%}
                    {{
                      block.settings.image
                      | image_url: width: 1000
                      | image_tag:
                        class: 'c-product-atc-offer__supplement-image',
                        loading: 'lazy',
                        widths: '400, 600, 800, 1000',
                        alt: block.settings.title | escape
                    }}
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {%- if block.settings.caption != blank -%}
                    <div class="c-product-atc-offer__image-caption">{{ block.settings.caption }}</div>
                  {%- endif -%}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        {%- endcase -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% style %}
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer {
    --product-atc-bg: {{ section.settings.background_color }};
    --product-atc-surface: {{ section.settings.media_background_color }};
    --product-atc-border: {{ section.settings.border_color }};
    --product-atc-text: {{ section.settings.text_color }};
    --product-atc-muted: {{ section.settings.muted_text_color }};
    --product-atc-accent: {{ section.settings.accent_color }};
    --product-atc-button-bg: {{ section.settings.button_background_color }};
    --product-atc-button-text: {{ section.settings.button_text_color }};
    --product-atc-message-success: {{ section.settings.success_color }};
    --product-atc-message-error: {{ section.settings.error_color }};
    background: var(--product-atc-bg);
    color: var(--product-atc-text);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__container {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: grid;
    gap: 36px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 1280px;
    padding: {{ section.settings.padding_top_mobile }}px 20px {{ section.settings.padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__media,
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__content {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__notice {
    align-items: center;
    background: {{ section.settings.notice_bg_color }};
    border-radius:  16px;
    bottom: 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    left: 0;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__notice-icon {
    color: {{ section.settings.notice_text_color }};
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 0;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__notice-icon svg {
    display: block;
    height: 28px;
    width: 28px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__notice-copy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__notice-eyebrow {
    color: {{ section.settings.notice_text_color }};
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    opacity: 0.7;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 120%; /* 16.8px */
    letter-spacing: 2.1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__notice-body {
    color: {{ section.settings.notice_text_color }};
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__media-card {
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--product-atc-surface);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 320px;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 24px;
    position: relative;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__image {
    display: block;
    height: auto;
    max-width: 100%;
    width: 100%;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__image--placeholder {
    width: 100%;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__empty-state {
    background: rgba(213, 79, 47, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(213, 79, 47, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-family: "TT Commons", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding: 16px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__pill-wrap {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__pill {
    display: inline-block;
    background: {{ section.settings.pill_bg_color }};
    color: {{ section.settings.pill_text_color }};
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-family: "TT Commons", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2.1px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    padding: 10px 22px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__reviews {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__reviews-fallback {
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--product-atc-accent);
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-family: "TT Commons", sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    gap: 8px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__stars {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__stars svg {
    display: block;
    height: 14px;
    width: 14px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__reviews-rating,
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__reviews-count {
    color: var(--product-atc-accent);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-product-atc-offer__reviews-app,
